WEBVTT

00:00:06.919 --> 00:00:09.839
High above the floor 
of Nevada’s Black Canyon,

00:00:09.839 --> 00:00:12.633
a group of men repelled
down the cliff face.

00:00:12.884 --> 00:00:16.429
Suddenly, a man stumbled 
over the canyon rim.

00:00:16.429 --> 00:00:19.515
He plummeted past the men, 
too fast for them to grab—

00:00:19.515 --> 00:00:22.268
when another climber swung 
out from the rocks

00:00:22.268 --> 00:00:23.853
and carried him to safety.

00:00:24.353 --> 00:00:26.939
Once they’d repelled 
the engineer up the cliff,

00:00:26.939 --> 00:00:30.109
his savior swung back to business
as usual—